{"id":9,"jsonrpc":"2.0","result":{"contents":{"kind":"markdown","value":"Declared in: Base.cj  \nPackage info: default  \n\n```cangjie\ninternal let errY: Int64 = 1.0 + 3\n```\n\n---\n\n浮点数不能够自动转化为整数 所以此处会有诊断报错  \n\n\nerr Float cannot transport to Int64  \n"},"range":{"end":{"character":16,"line":33},"start":{"character":12,"line":33}}}}